Naming convention:
  YYYYMMDD_Device_UseCase.csv

20191001
  BeeWi (SmartLight)
    ON = 5 sec calm, switch on bulb, 5 sec calm
    ON + OFF = 5 sec calm, switch on bulb, 5 sec calm, switch off bulb, 5 sec calm
    COLOUR = 5 sec calm, turn on detailed settings, switch to RGB, change colour, turn off detailed settings, 5 sec calm
    PASSIVE = 10 sec calm
    OFF = 5 sec calm, switch off bulb, 5 sec calm
    LongConn = 5 sec calm, turn on detailed settings, keep changing settings for about 40 sec, turn off detailed settings, 5 sec calm
